23	5	3	Add apples and return to a boil. Reduce heat, cover, and simmer until apples are tender, 6 to 8 minutes. Cool for 30 minutes.	\N	\N
24	5	4	Ladle into 5 freezer containers, leaving 1/2 inch of headspace. Cool at room temperature no longer than 1 1/2 hours.	\N	\N
25	5	5	Seal and freeze. Can be stored for up to 12 months.	\N	\N
